                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>New Orls</placeName>\n                <date>May 2. 5609</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>My dear friend.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">It is a singular fact that your form of<lb/>\n                <hi rend=\"underline\"><date>March 19</date></hi> only reached me a few days ago,\n                which accounts<lb/> for the inquiries which I made in a late letter &amp; to\n                which<lb/> you reply in yours of <hi rend=\"underline\"><date>April 3d</date></hi>\n                remarking that you had<lb/> previously answered me. Let that pass</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">My main object just now in addressing you is to<lb/> say that as\n                soon as I hear from you of a day being<lb/> freed for the c<add>?</add> at\n                    <placeName>New York</placeName> I shall make final<lb/> arrangements for my\n                departure <del>passage</del>. The secretary<lb/> of the congregation informed you\n                immediately of my appoint<lb/>ment as the Delegate. I shall leave here so as to<lb/>\n                be in <placeName>NYork</placeName> by the <date>11th</date> proxo unless I hear that\n                the day<lb/> has been postponed. I suppose the Occident of<lb/> the <date>1st</date>\n                will satisfy me that the convention will be held<lb/> &amp; as soon as that is recd.\n                I may start. In your<lb/> last No you talk of <hi rend=\"underline\">many</hi>\n                delegates from the same<lb/> congregation. Of course each <hi rend=\"underline\"\n                    >Congregation</hi> can only have<lb/>\n                <hi rend=\"underline\">one vote</hi> &amp; even as to delegates, if one congregation\n                is<lb/> allowed too many, the delegates from some may not<lb/> get a chance to say a\n                word. Look to this in time.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Respecting the inside furniture of the Synagogue<lb/> here, you can\n                take your time &amp; need not <add>?</add><lb/> to ship anything altho' what you may\n                have sent<lb/> will be taken care of by <persName>Mr Touro</persName> till my\n                return<lb/> Perhaps you may like me &amp; see some of the</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p33n2113j/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
