              "items": [
                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p33n2113j/manifest/annotation/p2",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>“fixings” &amp; the longer certain good are kept out of<lb/> this climate (until they\n                are used) the better. As regards<lb/> more money you had best write direct to\n                    <persName>Mr Touro</persName> at<lb/> once, as he is <hi rend=\"underline\">very\n                    slow</hi> &amp; you can say that as you<lb/> presume I am absent starting you\n                address him instead<lb/> of me. by the bye, say a word to him upon the\n                importance<lb/> of this convention &amp; the propriety of each congregation\n                sending<lb/> a proper delegate so that whatever expenses may grow<lb/> out of the\n                convention he may not think the means of<lb/> the congregation are squandered.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I hope to meet <persName>Mr. Gutheim</persName> this summer<lb/>\n                perhaps at the convention or if I take the <placeName>Sandusky</placeName><lb/>\n                route north I may see him in <placeName>Cincinnati</placeName></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I am altogether undetermined which may I shall<lb/> go, perhaps\n                direct to <placeName>NY</placeName> by steamship hence on the<lb/>\n                <date>21st</date> inst or on the <date>1st</date> proximo, be to\n                    <placeName>Savannah</placeName> by<lb/> mail &amp; thence by steamer to\n                    <placeName>NY</placeName> or I may pass through<lb/> to\n                    <placeName>Charleston</placeName> &amp; there take steam. My movements will\n                depend<lb/> upon my time, &amp; the company of my respectable delegates<lb/> that I\n                may fall in with.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I do not know if it will scarcely be worth while<lb/> for you to\n                answer this letter, but still as I shall not<lb/> in all probability leave here\n                before <date>20th</date> perhaps it will be as well<lb/> for you to do so in case\n                you have anything to say of moment</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">If you wish to see me before we meet at the convention<lb/> write to\n                me here <del>as ever</del> at once. I should like to have<lb/> talk with you in\n                advance of any caucusing, but</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p33n2113j/canvas/p2"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
